Class OrderItem

java.lang.Object
OrderItem
public class OrderItem extends Object
OrderItem class represents a single item in an order, such as "Taro Milk Tea" or "Black Tea." It includes information about the item's ID, name, size, price, quantity, toppings, ice level, sugar level, series, and ingredients.
Author:
Hyder Ochsner
